{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"e3be118bd8","title":"对王海容来信的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0536b8bf5e","index":0,"year":1964,"month":9,"day":30,"articleId":"e3be118bd8"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji47","name":"毛泽东全集第47卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/47-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji47":{"comments":[{"id":"505be5e980","publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"e3be118bd8","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"在北京外国语学院进修英语的王海容1964年9月28日写信给毛泽东，反映对学院教学改革的一些意见，说：“在改革的某些具体做法上或某些措施上还有不少的偏差，存在一定的问题，我认为如果现在不及时纠正，那么将影响学生全面地掌握知识。"},{"id":"96a810aacc","publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"e3be118bd8","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"本篇一写在王海容来信的信封上；本篇二写在王海容来信的第一页上；本篇三写在来信的第二页反映外国语学院教学改革中存在问题的那段话旁。"},{"id":"82cd6ba5f3","publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"e3be118bd8","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"陆定一，当时任中共中央书记处书记、中央宣传部部长。"}],"contents":[{"id":"a890076d3c","type":"title","text":"对王海容来信的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"e3be118bd8"},{"id":"505be5e980","type":"paragraph","text":"送陆定一同志的处","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"e3be118bd8"},{"id":"96a810aacc","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东定一同志：","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"e3be118bd8"},{"id":"82cd6ba5f3","type":"paragraph","text":"这封信有些事值得注意，在第二页上，请看一看。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"e3be118bd8"},{"id":"2e9449976f","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"e3be118bd8"},{"id":"bde6a14284","type":"paragraph","text":"九月册日","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"e3be118bd8"},{"id":"def7c6d909","type":"paragraph","text":"此人叫王海容，是个女孩子，很有些志气，是人民代表王季范的孙女儿，也是我的外孙女儿。你如果想找她谈谈，可叫我的秘书徐业夫送她去。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"e3be118bd8"},{"id":"1b08139eb1","type":"subtitle","text":"又及三","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"e3be118bd8"},{"id":"303c8d41c2","type":"paragraph","text":"请派人调查一下，及时改正。","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"e3be118bd8"}],"page":{"id":"95dbf2028a","publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"e3be118bd8","start":177,"end":178}}}},"__N_SSG":true}